{"tid":1838012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得香港根本有過百單武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-01-24T00:52:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T10:18:53.000Z","uid":125168,"like":708,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"2736edeb45d1a3c50ab84085b80e1299dccd75ba","tid":1838012,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:52:35.000Z","msg":"但只要政府死都唔認，其他全部係高度懷疑，我地就會掉以輕心。日日望到支那咁多案例一d都唔爽，只會令我諗起香港有幾多嘢同支那一樣瞞報<br />\n<br />\n戴口罩，勤洗手呀，港共無當過我地條命係一回事"},{"pid":"24365b03ce2313f4bb4a528517c13e8cecd37a4a","tid":1838012,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92338d45393e12536e9e436e0686ba44c1f7174e","tid":1838012,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd39e00a8918bd23fd259f9ad0015246071d4da","tid":1838012,"uid":200165,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkhubei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkhubei%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=d822fac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkhubei/</a><br />\n<br />\n叫佢地出黎找數啦"},{"pid":"9e775df50aec06fc53238c74c1db3e58d5e19793","tid":1838012,"uid":147376,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我懷疑已經社區爆發</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2f8811dab274ba3cbc6a0e745453d738dcfed69e","tid":1838012,"uid":200165,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:57:25.000Z","msg":"香港湖北社團總會&middot;<br />\n  <br />\n香港湖北社團總會是由原&ldquo;香港湖北聯誼會&rdquo;更名而來。<br />\n宗旨是：團結愛祖國、愛香港、愛湖北的人士；促進港、澳、台、海外地區與湖北省及內地的經濟、技術、文化等方面的交流；促進香港繁榮、穩定；促進會員之間相互溝通、增進友誼。<br />\n香港湖北聯誼會于1994年正式在香港註冊成立。由旅居港澳地區的湖北人以及對湖北有深厚感情、關心湖北發展建設的熱心人士發起成立。是一個踐行愛祖國愛香港愛湖北崇高使命的非營利性社團。<br />\n自成立以來，致力促進香港的經濟繁榮、社會和諧，關心、支援湖北的建設和發展，為促進鄂港經濟、文化和技術交流與合作做了大量卓有成效的工作，積極發揮了鄂港的橋樑和紐帶作用。<br />\n因應不斷發展壯大，香港湖北聯誼會於2018年4月25日正式更名為&ldquo;香港湖北社團總會&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n香港湖北社團總會地址：<br />\n <br />\n 九龍荔枝角道838號勵豐中心705-706室(近荔枝角地鐵站D2出口)<br />\n電話：（852）2724 6384<br />\n傳真：（852）2372 9092<br />\n電郵：info@hubei.com.hk"},{"pid":"58a817a2367a7da906426b7676aed80fe5548a2b","tid":1838012,"uid":49908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fd39e00a8918bd23fd259f9ad0015246071d4da","tid":1838012,"uid":200165,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkhubei/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkhubei%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=d822fac9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkhubei/</a><br />\n<br />\n叫佢地出黎找數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c006a666699c996238e0c29501c1172d6eade8","tid":1838012,"uid":39383,"like":6,"dislike":39,"score":-33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"香港資訊較流通, 呢d未必呃到人"},{"pid":"04dc496a01a2ebdbebba40c8857640c401425af2","tid":1838012,"uid":247184,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:59:49.000Z","msg":"潛伏期成兩個禮拜，下兩星期開始見真章"},{"pid":"5e9e2c00e337b21383870a4ac046dfddafcf7cdf","tid":1838012,"uid":125168,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"c0c006a666699c996238e0c29501c1172d6eade8","tid":1838012,"uid":39383,"like":6,"dislike":39,"score":-33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:58:09.000Z","msg":"香港資訊較流通, 呢d未必呃到人"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T00:59:59.000Z","msg":"831無死人"},{"pid":"06b0ac6616277da8d84067be646b30da5f1833dc","tid":1838012,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"q